This repository contains a Python script for analyzing and forecasting energy consumption using ARIMA (AutoRegressive Integrated Moving Average) time series modeling.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ“ˆ Time series visualization and decomposition  
- ğŸ“Š Stationarity testing (Augmented Dickey-Fuller test)  
- ğŸ” ACF/PACF plotting for ARIMA parameter selection  
- ğŸ§  ARIMA model fitting and forecasting  
- ğŸ“‰ Model evaluation (MSE, RMSE)  
- ğŸ”® Forecast visualization  

---

## ğŸ“¦ Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- Required packages:

```bash
pandas
numpy
