---

## âš™ï¸ Customization

Modify these parameters in `main()`:

```python
# ARIMA order (p,d,q)
order = (1, 1, 1)  

# Seasonal period (for decomposition)
period = 12  

# Forecast horizon
forecast_steps = 10
```

